具体实现步骤如下：

1. 创建一个实现了`com.alibaba.excel.write.handler.WriteCellStyleHandler`接口的类，重写`cellStyle(int rowNum, int cellNum)`方法，在该方法中设置水印的样式，如下代码：

```java
import com.alibaba.excel.write.handler.WriteCellStyleHandler;
import org.apache.poi.ss.usermodel.*;

public class WaterMarkHandler implements WriteCellStyleHandler {

    @Override
    public void cellStyle(CellStyle cellStyle, Cell cell, Head head, int rowNum, int cellNum) {
        if (rowNum == 0 && cellNum == 0) { // 只在第一个单元格中添加水印
            // 添加水印
            Drawing<?> drawing = cell.getSheet().createDrawingPatriarch();
            CreationHelper creationHelper = cell.getSheet().getWorkbook().getCreationHelper();
            Font font = cell.getSheet().getWorkbook().createFont();
            font.setColor(IndexedColors.GREY_50_PERCENT.getIndex());
            font.setItalic(true);
            font.setBold(true);
            int x = 0, y = 0;  // 将水印放置在第一个单元格的左上角，可以自行调整位置
            drawing.createTextbox(new XSSFClientAnchor(x, y, x + 5, y + 5, (short) 0, 0, (short) 1, 1))
                    .setString(creationHelper.createRichTextString("REGISTERED COPY - FOR EVALUATION ONLY"))
                    .setVerticalAlignment(VerticalAlignment.CENTER)
                    .setHorizontalAlignment(HorizontalAlignment.CENTER)
                    .setShapeType(ShapeTypes.TEXT_BOX)
                    .getOrCreateRichTextRun()
                    .setFont(font);
        }
    }

    @Override
    public void comment(String s, Comment comment, Cell cell, Head head, int rowNum, int cellNum) {
        // Do nothing
    }

    @Override
    public void cellValue(Cell cell, Head head, Object value, int rowNum, int cellNum) {
        // Do nothing
    }
}
```

2. 通过`ExcelWriterSheetBuilder.registerWriteCellStyleHandler()`方法将该handler注册到Sheet对象上，如下代码：

```java
public static void main(String[] args) {
    String fileName = "test.xlsx";
    // 创建ExcelWriter对象
    ExcelWriter excelWriter = EasyExcel.write(fileName).build();
    // 得到写入Sheet对象
    WriteSheet writeSheet = EasyExcel.writerSheet("sheet1").build();
    // 在Sheet上注册水印handler
    writeSheet.registerWriteCellStyleHandler(new WaterMarkHandler());
    // 写入数据
    excelWriter.write(data(), writeSheet);
    // 关闭writer
    excelWriter.finish();
}
```

以上实现方式，可以向Excel文件的第一个单元格中添加一个“REGISTERED COPY - FOR EVALUATION ONLY”的水印，可以自行调整水印样式和位置。

